description:
Stampin' Ground was a hardcore-metalcore band from Cheltenham, UK active from 1995 to 2006. The band had toured with the likes of Anthrax, The Haunted, Agnostic Front, Sick of it All, Soulfly and played the main stage at Download Festival 2003.
